WorkItem.Description:
I always get this error when I click

    1. Button Add to Chart
    2. Menu Admin
    3. Button Log On
    4. Button Register
    5. Button CheckOut

I Use MVC Music Store v3.0b,  hope this can be fix and solution explain how to solve this issue
WorkItem.Summary: Microsoft JScript runtime error: Object expected

Comments.Message: Check the script tags in the views (e.g. ShoppingCart/Index.cshtml).  They may be linking to non-existent jquery versions.  I found jquery-1.4.4.min.js which is not in the 'Scripts' folder where I found jquery-1.5.1.min.js instead.  Do a global find and replace to correct the views.  After I did this all is well.  Hope this helps.
Note to developer:  maybe pulling js libraries from a CDN would be better than hard coding the links.
